title: Lien Sale By order of lien: Accepting bids on a 2001
text:
Lien Sale By order of lien: Accepting bids on a 2001 ad date: 10/24/2015 
Lien Sale By order of lien: Accepting bids on a 2001 Nissan Sentra, prior owner Velasco Salvador, and a 1988 BMW, prior owner Wesley Griffith. Vehicles may be seen at 17496 Carpenterville Road in Brookings, OR. Bids accepted through October 28, 2015 at 4:00p.m. We reserve the right to refuse any and all bids. Publish October 24 and 28, 2015 No. 71112562
